title: Celldweller - 2008 Soundtrack For The Voices In My Head Vol. 01
description:
Got my copy of the new CD in the mail today and feel i just MUST share a high quality copy, ripped in 320kbps MP3 right after pulled out of the package, no extra encoding, no tinkering, no gimmicks, no archives... just straight up SIMPLE ripping!!!
